name: IsCaltrainLate(UnofficialApp)
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: train status
Developer Terms of Use
des: Ever get to a Caltrain station just to find out that the trains are all shut down? Or worse, see that the next train will be there in "5 minutes," only to find out that they've been saying that for the last hour? Instead, you can ask Alexa for train statuses using this simple, unofficial, skill which crowdsources delay information.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
